0 x13 h6 y4af ff14 fs4 fc3 sc0 ls9 ws6">talents, abilities, and material possessions.</div><div class="t m0 x4f h52 y4b1 ff15 fs4 fc3 sc0 ls2 ws9a">Read again the texts for today. Which ones touch you the most, </div><div class="t m0 x4f h52 y4b2 ff15 fs4 fc3 sc0 ls2 ws31">and why? What motivates you to try to live a life that involves </div><div class="t m0 x4f h52 y4b3 ff15 fs4 fc3 sc0 ls2 ws60">seeking the good of others, as well as your own good? Why is it </div><div class="t m0 x4f h52 y592 ff15 fs4 fc3 sc0 ls2 ws6">so important for you, spiritually, to live for others?</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
